data.description: MUST SEE! This wonderful 2,088 sq ft, 3 bed, 2 bath, 2 car garage, single family home is on a cul-de-sac. This home boasts plenty of windows and natural light throughout the formal living room, family room, and dining room. The Master bedroom features 2 walk-in closets and a spacious master bath with garden tub and separate shower. Beautiful large kitchen has been completely renovated all brand new stainless steel appliances, installed a year ago, double sinks, and pantry. Newly installed premium quality carpets. This home is pre-wired for alarm monitoring and includes brand new front load high capacity washer & dryer.  Huge and convenient driveway with 2 car garage will provide excellent parking space for you and your guests. Enjoy privacy at its finest with no rear neighbors and overlooking the conservation as this home sits on 1.57 Acres of land! Don't miss this well-kept home that's ready for Move In!
